display_name: Immediate-Release Ccbs (Nifir Or Dihir Or Verir Or Dltir) (SHHS2)
description: Participant taking IMMEDIATE-RELEASE CCBS = NIFIR OR DIHIR OR VERIR OR DLTIR within two weeks of the SHHS2 visit.  All medications were recorded during the interview, and medication information was later categorized by physician review.
